  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a Genjutsu Specialist, you gain the following class features.</p><h3>Hit Points</h3><p><strong>Hit Dice</strong>: 1d6 per Genjutsu Specialist level<br /><strong>Hit Points</strong> at 1st Level and beyond: 6 + your constitution modifier<br /><strong>Hit Points at Higher Levels</strong>: 1d6 (or 4) + your constitution modifier per Genjutsu Specialist level after 1st</p><hr /><h3>Chakra Points</h3><p><strong>Chakra Dice</strong>: 1d12 per Genjutsu Specialist level<br /><strong>Chakra Points</strong> at 1st Level: 12 + your constitution modifier<br /><strong>Chakra Points at Higher Levels</strong>: 1d12 (or 7) + your Constitution modifier per Genjutsu Specialist level after 1st.</p><hr /><h3>Proficiencies</h3><p><strong>Armor</strong>: Light armor<br /><strong>Weapons</strong>: Simple Weapons<br /><strong>Ninja Tools</strong>: Disguise Kit, Poison Kit<br /><strong>Saving Throws</strong>: Constitution, Wisdom, Charisma<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: Illusions, Choose three from Chakra Control, Deception, History, Insight, Intimidation, Investigation, Perception, Persuasion, Stealth</p><h1>Genjutsu Specialist Advancement</h1><table><thead><tr><th>Level</th><th>Proficiency Bonus</th><th>Features</th><th>Malleable Mirages</th><th>Jutsu Known</th><th>Highest Rank Jutsu Known</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1st</td><td>+3</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.n5eb.class.Item.9eaUSxgdlllEhJPt]{Chakra Disruption} , @UUID[Compendium.n5eb.class.Item.WOhaRe7Pr9nrecxL]{Actualization}</td><td>—</td><td>6</td><td>D-Rank</td></tr><tr><td>2nd</td><td>+3</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.n5eb.class.Item.IDPKfoanfHcvUD4R]{Genjutsu Pledge}, @UUID[Compendium.n5eb.class.Item.Pn2P4Tusm2MsudlY]{Malleable Mirages}</td><td>2</td><td>7</td><td>D-Rank</td></tr><tr><td>3rd</td><td>+3</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.n5eb.class.Item.wj2aU5tv40Qiu89C]{Genjutsu Inception}</td><td>2</td><td>8</td><td>D-Rank</td></tr><tr><td>4th</td><td>+4</td><td>Ability Score Improvement/Feat</td><td>3</td><td>8</td><td>C-Rank</td></tr><tr><td>5th</td><td>+4</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.n5eb.class.Item.POGdngRz8vBrQKVF]{Real World Conversion}, @UUID[Compendium.n5eb.class.Item.HqUIDO7EVjnvTke6]{Keen Awareness}</td><td>3</td><td>9</td><td>C-Rank</td></tr><tr><td>6th</td><td>+4</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.n5eb.class.Item.IDPKfoanfHcvUD4R]{Genjutsu Pledge (2)}</td><td>4</td><td>10</td><td>C-Rank</td></tr><tr><td>7th</td><td>+5</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.n5eb.class.Item.wj2aU5tv40Qiu89C]{Genjutsu Inception (2)}</td><td>4</td><td>11</td><td>C-Rank</td></tr><tr><td>8th</td><td>+5</td><td>Ability Score Improvement/Feat</td><td>5</td><td>11</td><td>C-Rank</td></tr><tr><td>9th</td><td>+5</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.n5eb.class.Item.POGdngRz8vBrQKVF]{Real World Conversion (2)}</td><td>5</td><td>12</td><td>B-Rank</td></tr><tr><td>10th</td><td>+6</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.n5eb.class.Item.IDPKfoanfHcvUD4R]{Genjutsu Pledge (3)}</td><td>6</td><td>13</td><td>B-Rank</td></tr><tr><td>11th</td><td>+6</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.n5eb.class.Item.HqUIDO7EVjnvTke6]{Keen Awareness (2)}, @UUID[Compendium.n5eb.class.Item.N1emRFvKhvazE6Zr]{The Turn}</td><td>6</td><td>14</td><td>B-Rank</td></tr><tr><td>12th</td><td>+6</td><td>Ability Score Improvement/Feat</td><td>7</td><td>14</td><td>B-Rank</td></tr><tr><td>13th</td><td>+7</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.n5eb.class.Item.N1emRFvKhvazE6Zr]{The Turn (2)}, @UUID[Compendium.n5eb.class.Item.OcK8fIXdy950aFsX]{Master of Illusion}</td><td>7</td><td>15</td><td>A-Rank</td></tr><tr><td>14th</td><td>+7</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.n5eb.class.Item.IDPKfoanfHcvUD4R]{Genjutsu Pledge (4)}</td><td>8</td><td>16</td><td>A-Rank</td></tr><tr><td>15th</td><td>+7</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.n5eb.class.Item.POGdngRz8vBrQKVF]{Real World Conversion (3)}, @UUID[Compendium.n5eb.class.Item.N1emRFvKhvazE6Zr]{The Turn}</td><td>8</td><td>17</td><td>A-Rank</td></tr><tr><td>16th</td><td>+8</td><td>Ability Score Improvement/Feat</td><td>9</td><td>17</td><td>A-Rank</td></tr><tr><td>17th</td><td>+8</td><td>—</td><td>9</td><td>18</